    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Validation evidence demonstrates that the CFD model reliably predicts hemolysis-relevant QoIs within the COU operating envelope. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Governing requirement document references ASME V&V 40-2018 as the applicable standard; assessment activities and acceptance criteria are fully compliant with that edition.",
